Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:31.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:37.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:43.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:49.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:02:06.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:13.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:20.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:25.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:32.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:43.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落是我们的宿敌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借由搜集四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量变得越来越大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他不只跟犬夜叉有仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管任何时候\N他都不会自己动手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是卑劣的利用其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了解开\N弥勒法师所中的风穴咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救出珊瑚的弟弟\N被奈落囚禁的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要尽快的找到奈落\N打败他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第80话 杀生丸和被掳的小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到那家伙的臭味了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风的味道变得不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲被人给掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚奈落的分身\N神乐突然出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小玲给抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管放一百万个心吧\N杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你肯乖乖听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证那个叫小玲的\N一定会平安的回到你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  又是你这个大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么?这次又想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也没有特别想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你肯帮我干掉犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了这么点小事\N需要这么大费周章吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会为了区区一个人类小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便乖乖地听命于你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就这么放弃小玲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷  你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究还是跟来了  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的\N闻到了奈落的味道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次让我抓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非砍死他不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落一直神神秘秘\N从没有现身过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被那个\N叫神乐的女人抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以  你不可以出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一出去\N马上会被他们撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说\N你也是被他们抓回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样我们一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是负责看住你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你叫什么名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是妖怪的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个人话怎么这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不说话好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷\N到底会不会来救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有什么打算嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你到底有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是奈落城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里根本就不像是一座城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道奈落故意用臭味引诱我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我知道奈落城的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引我杀生丸进到里面去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不用一点小手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你会不会\N乖乖自投罗网呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要找的小姑娘\N我不可能会把她藏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城堡到处都是瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不需要一分钟\N小姑娘就没气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位小姑娘\N我暂时把她安置在城外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你们可以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是专程来救小玲的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点至少你应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀生丸少爷\N一向都讨厌被人指挥的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既不会去杀犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会特地来救小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那显然是来杀我奈落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千方百计把我引来\N还在那里说风凉话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笔帐待会再慢慢跟你算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还得看你有没有命活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就让我陪你玩一玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得\N四魂之玉碎片就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在对面那座山上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片就在那座山上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们负责追踪四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜奈落城的工作就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的臭味突然之间消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道\N奈落城的结界又封闭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点又要找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤居然没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你休想跑掉  大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一路上真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就让我奈落\N好好的陪你玩个够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是一些没用的死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是你的原形吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的原形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  这是小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才正要开始玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想要\N我杀生丸这条命是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对奈落到底有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧  难道奈落这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片就在这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于被你感应到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说\N应该就在奈落城旁边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想碎片应该是一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是珊瑚的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀身体里面刚好有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道真的是琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜真的好甜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要不要再吃一片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随时都可以再去偷一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀你真的什么都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连自己的爸妈也不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道连自己的父母都会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是完全没印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候\N我会想起一些可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事\N是你自己不愿意去回想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸妈妈还有我哥哥他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全家人都被强盗杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到现在还常常梦到他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吵对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没出声  是不是觉得我很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经好久\N没有跟人说这么多话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人的样子我一直都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来都没有忘掉过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子已经完全不记得\N自己做过些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经彻底毁在我的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后他什么都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他死其实对他是一种解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个下流的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒要看看你有什么能耐\N碰我杀生丸一根指头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒要仔细瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样的滥招数\N能玩到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下来的这一片片肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会变成我身上的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落正在吸收杀生丸的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它变成自己身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会突然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然在这里消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说这里是奈落城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股毒气跟瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是奈落的结界了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了  终于看到奈落城了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么人\N在城外破坏我的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐  马上去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有贵客到了  奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个客人也真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老远专程来拜访你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果\N他恐怕没机会见到你活着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就大功告成了  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻就会被我这块肉消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N你会变成我身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙的刀锋变成红色了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你破坏结界的是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还需要问吗  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N你已经不够资格跟我较量了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你快点滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在那里  小心被我给砍死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万别跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要让你尝尝我的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我跟你\N得好好打一场才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐之风一点杀气都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想不想打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一点都使不上劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎被他看穿我毫无斗志了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只好先在这挡一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是一些笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:22:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我太高估他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开  你们这帮妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以现在的犬夜叉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以打败奈落才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真是这样\N我就可以重获自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:40.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:47.20,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:54.02,ED,,0,0,0,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:24:01.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:07.32,ED,,0,0,0,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:14.40,ED,,0,0,0,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:21.15,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:27.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.25,0:24:34.82,ED,,0,0,0,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.97,0:24:41.50,ED,,0,0,0,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.80,0:24:48.12,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:54.75,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.65,0:24:58.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我失算
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.60,0:25:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到犬夜叉\N会采取这样的攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.11,0:25:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我非打败你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.87,0:25:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.01,0:25:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奈落已经完全得到\N杀生丸身上的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.95,0:25:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为\N那么容易可以打败我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.55,0:25:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说…杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.82,0:25:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚你有多少能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.02,0:25:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你同样\N要成为我肉体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.79,0:25:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.32,0:25:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落大坏蛋下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.26,0:25:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  马上给我杀了小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
